                                        <p>您的确认号码是<span class="text-primary font700">9977234</span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="confirmation-content">
                                    <div class="section-title text-left">
                                        <h4>预订信息</h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="book-sum-list">
                                        <li><span class="font600">预订号码: </span>9977234</li>
