                                            <ul class="help-list">
                                                <li><span class="font600">Hotline</span>:17521546355</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sidebar-module">
                                        <h4 class="heading mt-0">为什么要和我们预订？</h4>
                                        <div class="sidebar-module-inner">
                                            <ul class="featured-list-sm">
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up"></i></span>
                                                    <h6 class="heading mt-0">没有预订费用</h6>
                                                    我们向您预订酒店房间不收取额外费用
