                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i></span>
                                                    <h6 class="heading mt-0">没有取消看见</h6>
                                                    如果计划变更，我们不会向您收取取消或修改费用
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-inbox"></i></span>
                                                    <h6 class="heading mt-0">即时确认</h6>
                                                    即时预订确认无论是在线预订还是通过电话预订
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i></span>
                                                    <h6 class="heading mt-0">灵活预订</h6>
                                                    您可以提前一年预订或直至您入住的那一刻预订
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- end Main Wrapper -->
    </div>  <!-- end Container Wrapper -->
    <!-- start Back To Top -->
    <div id="back-to-top">
        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i></a>
    </div>
    <!-- end Back To Top -->
